name: the Clown by Lohas Queen
description:
I love clowns, because in this world, you have to be a clown a lot of the time.
The clown always brings laughters around, but he's always a bit sad inside, for the people who have not found true happiness. And he's sad sometimes because he misses his real home, so far away.
But, he heeps all his silent tears inside, and he loves making people happy.

he is 72cm tall, 20cm wide. Stuffed with pure cotton.
Made in a smoke free, vegan home.

Handmade by Lohas Queen.
